 ```
 
+Keep git wrapper output out of generated plugin scripts.
+
+```zsh
+% function git { print 'wrapper progress'; print -ru2 'wrapper diagnostic'; mockgit "$@" }
+% antidote-script fakeuser/fakerepo >$T_TEMPDIR/plugin.zsh 2>$T_TEMPDIR/git.log
+% cat $T_TEMPDIR/plugin.zsh | subenv ANTIDOTE_HOME
+fpath+=( "$ANTIDOTE_HOME/fakeuser/fakerepo" )
+source "$ANTIDOTE_HOME/fakeuser/fakerepo/fakerepo.plugin.zsh"
+% cat $T_TEMPDIR/git.log
+# antidote cloning fakeuser/fakerepo...
+wrapper progress
+wrapper diagnostic
+%
+```
+
+Git failures still fail script generation without writing to stdout.
+
+```zsh
+% function git { print 'wrapper progress'; print -ru2 'wrapper diagnostic'; return 23 }
+% antidote-script missing/repo >$T_TEMPDIR/plugin.zsh 2>$T_TEMPDIR/git.log  #=> --exit 1
+% test ! -s $T_TEMPDIR/plugin.zsh  #=> --exit 0
+% cat $T_TEMPDIR/git.log
+# antidote cloning missing/repo...
+wrapper progress
+wrapper diagnostic
+% t_reset
+%
+```
